divs: Sighting Detailson feb.23,06 i took my two pups out at 11pm, for their last potty break before bed, they were aggitated, i looked up over the trees and saw a rectangle with red,blue greenand white lights aboutas long as my middle finger and did not appear to be moving. i hurried the pups back into the house turrned the lights out and when i looked back at the rectangle there were two of them now.
Summary: took pups out for potty break,at 11pm, they were aggitated, looked up and saw rectagular object with red,blue green and white lights duration one minute.
